Class QuadNull

  • java.lang.Object
    • QuadNull
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    QuadNode
    public class QuadNull
extends java.lang.Object
implements QuadNode
    QuadNull object implement QuadNode interface to represent the null node of PRQuadtree. QuadNull also implement the fly weight pattern for saving memory space.
    Version:
    2021-10-16
    Author:
    Ting-Jui Hsu
